        "Explicitly excluded from the initial scope were payroll integration, post-employment onboarding workflows, performance appraisal modules, and full enterprise PostgreSQL migration, although architectural provisions were made for future database integration. Mobile native applications were likewise out of scope; however, responsive web design was required to support mobile browser access. The scope statement was reviewed with HR stakeholders to confirm alignment with immediate operational needs.",
