        "Engagement strategies varied by stakeholder group. HR managers participated in requirements workshops and user acceptance testing. HR staff provided feedback on dashboard layout and workflow sequencing. Applicants were considered through usability principles applied to the careers portal design. External interviewers informed the design of simplified sign-in using name and panel access code. Audit stakeholders influenced the inclusion of comprehensive logging and non-repudiation of completed interview records.",
