        "Interview invitations were composed individually in email clients, sometimes resulting in inconsistent messaging or omission of key logistical details. Interview panels recorded scores on paper forms that were collected after sessions and manually averaged by HR staff. External interviewers experienced delays receiving credentials or instructions, and their marks occasionally arrived after selection meetings had already concluded.",
