        "HR routes under /hr render hr_dashboard.html with embedded sections for jobs, screening, interviews, interview marks, and settings modals. JSON endpoints support asynchronous interviewer management, link generation, interview lifecycle actions, scoring, screening, and selection. The interviewer routes implement join authentication and dashboard rendering filtered to active candidates. CV scoring integration calls services/cv_scoring.py during screening operations.",
